snippet.title: Sonic The Broad Jump
snippet.description:
It's a Sonic channel flash game where it used to be in Sonic channel, but due to it being taken down, and the waybackmachine, I decided to download the swf and upload it to mediafire here:

http://www.mediafire.com/file/gnko6o744m4wl33/Sonic+The+Broad+Jump.swf

It's perfectly functional for anyone who wants to play it on their flash player. I can't play other flash games on my laptop otherwise.
